<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تَنَافِيَ بَيْنَهُمَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(وَحَدُّ الْخَمْرِ وَ)</span> حَدُّ <span class="c2">(السُّكْرِ)</span> مِنْ غَيْرِ الْخَمْرِ (فِي الْحُرِّ ثَمَانُونَ سَوْطًا لِإِجْمَاعِ الصَّحَابَةِ <span class="special">﵃</span>،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>